  "detailed_description": "<strong><u>Gameplay</u></strong><br><br>In the Unknown You Will Roam Around Mysterious Dark Locations<br>Solving Mysteries , You Will Be Chased And Hunted By Monsters<br>Through The Night Battling Creatures and Solving The Current Objective<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/660bfdc33637c8eb806e613b23291d03.avif?t=1687088375\" width=600 height=270 /></span><br><br><br>Find Fuses to Unlock Doors and Weapon Crates, Ammo and Health to Survive<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/04d4c7c10ce0aba0993142e7d1ada2b8.poster.avif?t=1687088375\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/04d4c7c10ce0aba0993142e7d1ada2b8.webm?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/04d4c7c10ce0aba0993142e7d1ada2b8.mp4?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><u>Content</u></strong><br>The Unknown Currently Has 2 separate missions to capture 2 unique and Scary<br>Creatures. Each mission includes a unique environment, story, gameplay, and monsters.<br>Have fun with your friends trying to complete each Objective and <br>capture the supernatural Creatures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/64367cb60ad3ca467e584ef527597be6.poster.avif?t=1687088375\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/64367cb60ad3ca467e584ef527597be6.webm?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/64367cb60ad3ca467e584ef527597be6.mp4?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>STAY ALERT</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/f8e7464b3a6f1fc8a16342acea3c9a27.poster.avif?t=1687088375\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/f8e7464b3a6f1fc8a16342acea3c9a27.webm?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/f8e7464b3a6f1fc8a16342acea3c9a27.mp4?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><u>Key Features</u></strong><br>- Up to 4 Player Online Co-op<br>  Play Together With Your Friends To Survive<br><br>- Immersive Experience<br>  Realistic graphics and sounds as well as having minimal user <br>  interfaces will ensure a totally immersive experience that will<br>  keep you on your toes.<br><br> -Loot Crates<br>  There are Loot Crate all Around the Map Arm Yourself<br><br>-Proximity Voice Chat<br> Nothing Better than Hearing Your Friends Scream In Distance<br><br>-Scaling Difficulty <br> The Creatures Will get Stronger as the Game Progresses<br><br>-Replayabililty<br> Multiple Missions Multiple Creatures And More Creatures/Missions<br> Will be Added as Time Goes one<br><br>-Respawn: The game incorporate a creative and dynamic <br> way to respawn, you will able to respawn up to 3 times.<br><br><br><br>And More Creatures Will Be Added Soon <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/618f93c27e8edf7bccfe93b4cb17d851.avif?t=1687088375\" width=600 height=270 /></span><br><br><br><strong><u>Development RoadMap</u></strong><br>I Want to Keep Improving the Game Polishing and<br>Adding New Content to the Game Including<br><br>-New Monsters( Based on Childhood Classics and <strong>Creepy Pasta Monsters</strong> )<br><br>-More Environments<br><br>-New Puzzles <br><br>-Improved Gameplay<br><br>-New Weapions<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/74c288afcc89d481574a4c9de30dcb08.poster.avif?t=1687088375\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/74c288afcc89d481574a4c9de30dcb08.webm?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234550/extras/74c288afcc89d481574a4c9de30dcb08.mp4?t=1687088375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
